A collection of basic algorithms implemented in C created while I took COMP10002 (Foundations of Algorithms).

Implemented so far:

Sorting Algorithms:
- Quicksort
- Bubble Sort
- Insertion Sort
- Heapsort
- Bogosort
- Mergesort

Search:
- Linear Search
- Binary Search

Pattern Search:
- Naive Pattern Search
- Knuth Morris Pratt (KMP) 
- Boyer Moore Horspool (BMH)
- Suffix Array Pattern Search 

Graphs:
- BFS and DFS
